description:
Adds the character "Cosmonaut β."
Yesterday's enemies are today's friends!  The "Cosmonaut" alien joins the fight in a formal helmet suit. Undoubtedly a depenable ally from the start of the game!
Uses the same equipment, Abilities, and SP Move as the unhelmeted "Cosmonaut."
name: "Additional character" Cosmonaut β, Wearing a Helmet: Reskin
